ation pune india certifications certified scrum professionalcertified scrummastercertified scrum product owner credentials added qualifications scaling scrum fundamentals  biography dharmesh shah agile coach seeing many companies struggling with the implementation of the agile methodology decided to move to training and coaching to help teams adopt lean and agile principles and reap the benefit as i see the problem is not the lack of will on part of the company but while implementing only few processes and the focus on the principles is lost this is due to the lack of indepth knowledge of lean and agile along with poor training here’s summary of overall experience •    firm believer and applying lean and agile principles since  years and certified scrum master since  years  •    championed and transitioned multiple product groups to agile methodology using scrum the teams were spread across geographies of sizes  to  people and revenues ranging from  to  million this resulted in improved quality predictability and team morale •    experienced in conducting practical based agile and lean trainings from engineers to the top management •    in addition to being a scrum master have been the scrum coach for  years guiding scrum masters and team in implementing lean and agile principles •     years of diverse software industry experience with startups as well as large companies globally •    the career journey started as a programmer and moving up the ladder to technical lead architect manager and program manager while working on various different technologies and domains   work experience cisco agile coachapril   present pune mh indiaworking as a agile coach and following are the responsibilities • as part of the agile coaches team responsible for the agile transformation using scrum for the mobile business unit within cisco  agile coach for multiple scrum teams for the local site and guide them towards the successfully implementing the scrum practices  act as mentor to scrum masters product owners and leadership team  educate all levels and roles including senior leaders across the organization on agile principles processes practices and tools  conduct training workshops seminars as required on various detailed agile and scrum practices  share best practices with respect to agile software engineering practices  drive visibility of information that help the team see how they are doing  drive organization change needed to allow agile teams to excel  help remove impediments raised by the scrum team selfemployed agile trainer and consultantoctober   march  pune mh indiawith passion for agile and observing how the various companies are not implementing properly left the job and decided to help companies implement agile properly symantec sr princ program managerjune   september  pune mh indiaas a program manager responsible for making the product development practices to be more effective  part of the team for rolling out the agile across the product group of size  people  played various roles from development manager scrum master program manager during the transformation  also coaching and mentoring the scrum masters and teams for better implementation of agile articles ive written is agile a culture or a process these days everyone uses the word agile to mean different things to their own advantage find a course » certified scrummaster certified scrum product owner certified scrum developer certified agile leadership continuing education » virtual learning » find education providers » certified scrum trainer certified enterprise coach registered education provider   newsletter signup subscribe dharmesh shah – productcoalitioncomhomepagewrite a storysign in  sign updharmesh shahmedium member since mar foundercto of hubspot and blogger at onstartupscom followingk followersblockedunblockfollowfollowingstories inproductcoalitioncomother stories by dharmesh shahdharmesh shah hasn’t published in productcoalitioncom yet check back later to se